{"tid":1761413,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬克龍回應華為問題稱不會將特定公司污名化","createTime":"2019-11-29T02:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T03:36:20.000Z","uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7da8950ec6b582c1586283794c2b0db0ef8d69df","tid":1761413,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T02:02:32.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】法國總統馬克龍回應華為問題時稱，不會將特定公司污名化。<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍會見到訪法國的北約秘書長斯托爾滕貝格，二人其後一同見記者。被問到中國電訊設備製造商華為會否對法國構成安全風險，馬克龍回應稱，他從未想過將特定電訊設備營運商或國家污名化。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">法國電訊事務國務秘書早前表示，法國不會跟隨美國，不會將華為排除在當地的5G網絡建設之外。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=371625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D371625&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=442fbe71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D371625&h=f57e5039\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=371625</a>"},{"pid":"426c11eae3c428cbd82781767b07596c1c2f732b","tid":1761413,"uid":13303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T02:03:32.000Z","msg":"戴高樂聽到都激到返生"},{"pid":"c5f4699db59e9150da6433862e41782877914a81","tid":1761413,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T02:15:15.000Z","msg":"法包不嬲同美帝唔夾ga la"},{"pid":"19c4198f3b56bd8e6d5122e64d4e326906f5a434","tid":1761413,"uid":270905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T02:16:35.000Z","msg":"到時出事佢自己記住佢講既野"},{"pid":"84c935cbc918808441aaf176d17c09bdbead3cb9","tid":1761413,"uid":296369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T02:17:47.000Z","msg":"到時佢哋d國家機密比人偷晒，唔好怨......."},{"pid":"ce316cbdf0bd42ade67399d2ecaa5826693c6f61","tid":1761413,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T02:42:23.0